title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - November 9, 2021
itunes:title: Beyond A Reasonable Doubt - November 9, 2021
description:
Adam and Mark connect to talk about the latest developments in the Kyle Rittenhouse trial wherein the prosecution has rested their case as well as a pre-dawn FBI raid. 

Watch Beyond A Reasonable Doubt on YouTube at YouTube.com/ReasonableDoubtPodcast and subscribe while you're there.
